      "message": "correct, the scope of this task is to remove lint warnings not ensure full idempotency. This we can discuss separately. Any more objections to adding changed_when sugar here ? This   task always lead to \"change\". If helm env doesn't exists it will create it, if env exists update action is triggered which doesn't necessarily change anything but it's out of scope of this commit",
